Love is a verb.

711
00:34:18,953 --> 00:34:22,163
Love the feeling is a
fruit of love, the verb.

712
00:34:23,889 --> 00:34:25,132
(chuckling)

713
00:34:25,201 --> 00:34:26,201
Wait!

714
00:34:27,341 --> 00:34:28,618
