01:49:20,830 --> 01:49:22,970
Here, here will I remain.

2140
01:49:24,212 --> 01:49:26,939
With worms that are
thy chambermaids.

2141
01:49:27,008 --> 01:49:29,977
Here will I setup
my everlasting rest

2142
01:49:30,046 --> 01:49:32,911
and shake the yoke of
inauspicious stars!

2143
01:49:34,153 --> 01:49:36,121
Arms take your last embrace.

2144
01:49:39,849 --> 01:49:42,714
And lips, O you.

2145
01:49:42,783 --> 01:49:45,648
The doors of breath, seal
with a righteous kiss.

2146
01:49:45,717 --> 01:49:48,236
A dateless bargain
to engrossing death.

2147
01:49:48,305 --> 01:49:51,895
Come, bitter conduct.

2148
01:49:51,964 --> 01:49:54,139
Come unsavory guide.

2149
01:49:54,208 --> 01:49:57,004
Thou desperate pilot,
now at once run

2150
01:49:57,073 --> 01:49:59,731
on the dashing rocks
thy sea-sick weary bark!

2151
01:50:01,664 --> 01:50:02,699
Here's to my love.

2152
01:50:05,771 --> 01:50:08,532
(light music)

2153
01:50:15,091 --> 01:50:16,610
O, true apothecary.

2154
01:50:17,680 --> 01:50:18,715
Thy drugs are quick.

2155
01:50:18,784 --> 01:50:19,784
Does he feel guilt?

2156
01:50:21,131 --> 01:50:22,719
Pain?

2157
01:50:22,788 --> 01:50:24,134
Abandonment?

2158
01:50:27,448 --> 01:50:30,762
He doesn't die for her but
just to escape his own pain.

2159
01:50:32,211 --> 01:50:33,454
And is that love?

2160
01:50:35,249 --> 01:50:38,735
Or is it to still live and
to carry on her memory?

2161
01:50:40,495 --> 01:50:42,946
Love isn't something
that you find.

2162
01:50:43,982 --> 01:50:45,535
It's something that you choose.

2163
01:50:46,985 --> 01:50:50,644
And when you choose
it, love will find you.

2164
01:50:53,267 --> 01:50:54,406
Front and center.

2165
01:50:56,028 --> 01:50:58,790
(uplifting music)

2166
01:51:15,220 --> 01:51:16,221
(clicking)

2167
01:51:17,153 --> 01:51:18,153
(sighing)

2168
01:51:19,327 --> 01:51:21,951
(uplifting music)

2169
01:51:25,920 --> 01:51:26,920
(sighs)

2170
01:51:32,651 --> 01:51:33,825
Vincent?

2171
01:51:33,894 --> 01:51:35,550
Your mom's name
is Roxanne Stilwell.

2172
01:51:35,619 --> 01:51:36,966
What?

2173
01:51:37,035 --> 01:51:38,864
And she's looking for you.

2174
01:51:40,107 --> 01:51:42,592
(light music)

2175
01:51:51,359 --> 01:51:54,259
Valentina, I apologize
a thousand times

2176
01:51:55,605 --> 01:51:56,848
for the way I've treated you.

2177
01:51:58,435 --> 01:51:59,436
I should have listened.

2178
01:52:01,956 --> 01:52:04,131
Thus with a kiss,

2179
01:52:06,754 --> 01:52:07,754
I die!

2180
01:52:09,170 --> 01:52:11,621
(light music)

2181
01:52:17,282 --> 01:52:18,870
What's here?

2182
01:52:18,939 --> 01:52:22,597
A cup closed in my
true love's hand.

2183
01:52:24,979 --> 01:52:28,949
(uplifting, climatic music)

2184
01:52:29,018 --> 01:52:33,505
I don't want our
story to end in tragedy.

2185
01:52:33,574 --> 01:52:36,508
And left no friendly
drop to help me after?

2186
01:52:37,509 --> 01:52:40,339
(uplifting music)

2187
01:52:48,347 --> 01:52:49,347
(Juliet) O happy dagger,

2188
01:52:50,384 --> 01:52:52,662
this is thy sheath.

2189
01:52:54,215 --> 01:52:57,011
(uplifting music)

2190
01:53:04,881 --> 01:53:07,401
There rest and let me die.

2191
01:53:07,470 --> 01:53:09,921
(grunting)

2192
01:53:11,715 --> 01:53:13,062
Neither do I.

2193
01:53:21,691 --> 01:53:24,867
(patrons murmuring)

2194
01:53:24,936 --> 01:53:26,351
(gagging)

2195
01:53:26,420 --> 01:53:29,388
(patrons murmuring)

2196
01:53:33,392 --> 01:53:35,084
(screeching tires)

2197
01:53:36,257 --> 01:53:38,742
(light music)

2198
01:53:56,760 --> 01:53:58,314
(Vincent) Whoever reads this.

2199
01:53:59,936 --> 01:54:01,455
I mean every word.

2200
01:54:04,078 --> 01:54:05,700
I love you.

2201
01:54:05,769 --> 01:54:08,842
(uplifting music)

2202
01:54:08,911 --> 01:54:10,050
What do I mean by love?

2203
01:54:13,018 --> 01:54:14,018
That love is patient

2204
01:54:15,676 --> 01:54:17,195
and I will be patient with you.

2205
01:54:20,612 --> 01:54:21,612
Love is kind.

2206
01:54:25,686 --> 01:54:27,446
And kindness I'll give to you.

2207
01:54:34,798 --> 01:54:36,179
Love does not envy.

2208
01:54:42,427 --> 01:54:43,704
It does not boast.

2209
01:54:45,844 --> 01:54:48,329
(uplifting music)

2210
01:54:53,438 --> 01:54:54,438
It is not proud.

2211
01:54:56,648 --> 01:54:58,995
I will surrender
my pride for you.

2212
01:55:05,105 --> 01:55:07,314
Love does not dishonor others.

2213
01:55:14,286 --> 01:55:15,701
It is not self seeking.

2214
01:55:16,737 --> 01:55:19,222
(uplifting music building)

2215
01:55:22,846 --> 01:55:24,538
It is not easily angered.

2216
01:55:25,642 --> 01:55:27,610
It keeps no record of wrongs.

2217
01:55:34,651 --> 01:55:37,102
Love does not delight in evil.

2218
01:55:41,037 --> 01:55:42,797
But rejoices with the truth.

2219
01:55:44,420 --> 01:55:46,905
(uplifting music building)

2220
01:55:49,045 --> 01:55:51,427
Love always protects.

2221
01:55:56,225 --> 01:55:58,227
It always trusts.

2222
01:56:03,646 --> 01:56:06,925
And always hopes.

2223
01:56:10,791 --> 01:56:12,793
(climatic music)

2224
01:56:26,531 --> 01:56:28,429
Love always perseveres.

2225
01:56:31,087 --> 01:56:32,087
Charity?

2226
01:56:33,469 --> 01:56:35,954
(light music)

2227
01:56:37,611 --> 01:56:40,027
(whimpering)

2228
01:56:46,585 --> 01:56:48,829
(giggling)

2229
01:56:56,009 --> 01:56:58,321
(splashing)

2230
01:57:00,358 --> 01:57:02,843
(light music)

2231
01:57:24,037 --> 01:57:25,037
And love...

2232
01:57:26,798 --> 01:57:27,798
never...

2233
01:57:30,112 --> 01:57:31,044
fails.

2234
01:57:31,113 --> 01:57:33,943
(uplifting, climatic music)

2235
01:57:42,572 --> 01:57:43,572
Together.

2236
01:57:44,954 --> 01:57:47,819
(uplifting music)

2237
01:58:23,026 --> 01:58:25,581
(light music)

